results.name: Irregular triangle C(n,g) counting the connected 8-regular simple graphs on n vertices with girth exactly g.
comment: The first column is for girth at least 3. The row length is incremented to g-2 when 2n reaches A054760(8,g).

Triangular arrays C(n,g) counting connected simple k-regular graphs on n vertices with girth exactly g: A198303 (k=3), A184940 (k=4), A184950 (k=5), A184960 (k=6), A184970 (k=7), this sequence (k=8).
